description: Extension of Arundel Square gardens over railway and construction of 147 homes on south railway verge and derelict goods yard to a maximum of six  storeys plus basement accommodation and underground parking.
decision_conditions:
CONDITION:  The affordable housing shall be completed and handed over to a registered social landlord before 50% of the private residential units are occupied.

REASON:  To ensure the affordable housing element of the development is delivered within an acceptable time period in accordance with Policy H20 of the Unitary Development Plan 2002.
site_name: RAILWAY LAND, FROM ARUNDEL PLACE TO WESTBOURNE ROAD & 1-3
site_number: RAILWAY LAND, FROM ARUNDEL PLACE TO WESTBOURNE ROAD & 1-3
